platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Getting an idea out of your head and onto a screen can sometimes feel like trying to cross a deep canyon, but Forge helps bridge the gap between creativity and productivity. With an emphasis on quick sketching rather than full-fledged illustration, its clean design and perceptive controls let you quickly jot down and build upon concepts, making it perfect for turning a sprinkle of ideas into a full-fledged brainstorm.
